		<body>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>N.Y.</placeName> <date>Tuesday&#44; 4th of<lb/>Kislev &#40;November&#41; 1866</date>.</p>
				<p>To the learned Rabbi</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><addressee>Isaac Leeser</addressee>&#58;</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Herewith is the sum of &#36;37. Please<lb/> send me the books that are noted here below&#44;<lb/> and be good enough to let me know the<lb/> price of the Guide for Beginning to Teach<lb/> Small Children&#44; which I used to receive<lb/> through <persName>Dr. Bondi</persName>. I have forgotten<lb/> its price. It seems to me that he used<lb/> to charge me &#36; .30 Your Friend</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><persName role="author">H Sakolski</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><placeName>53 Division St.</placeName></p>
				<table rows="5" cols="3">
				<row>
				<cell>6 Prayer Books&#44; Ashkinazic &#64; 2.62&#189;</cell>
				<cell>21</cell>
				 <cell>15.75</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>3 prayer books Ashkinazic&#44; gilt &#64; 4.80</cell>
				<cell>18</cell>
				<cell>14.40</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>1 Bible &#40;English&#41;  &#64; 2.62</cell>
				<cell>3&#188;</cell>
				<cell>2.62</cell>
				</row>
