				</table>
				<p rend="Translator&#39;s note">The second column of figures &#40;in<lb/> different ink in original manuscript&#41; seems to have been<lb/> added by <persName>Leeser</persName>&#44; since they are in a<lb/> different hand&#44; either because they had<lb/> risen in price&#44; or because that is what<lb/> <persName>Leeser</persName> expected him to charge his customers.</p>
